F I've had a piece of peridot sitting around for a while, and even wrote a design for it a while back, but no matter 
F what I did, I just wasn't happy with it. This is the final design I'm going to write for it. It's my best barion trillion 
F yet! Works in materials from topaz to CZ (RI = 1.61 - 2.16) with no changes, but I prefer it in peridot.
F Suggested size = 6-12 mm
